oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Variety Attractions Job No. 38656
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Ritter, Tex;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 3177) for an order placed by Variety Attractions for 100 two color window cards for a performance by Tex Ritter at the Lawrence County Fair in Proctorville, Ohio on July 28. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
